## Task: Dark, clean app.css theme (no neon)
## Step: review

### src/app.css
```css
/* ── Dark, clean theme ── */

/* System font stack, reset body */
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Oxygen,
    Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", Arial,
    sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #e6e6e6;
  background: #1e1e1e;
}

/* Subtle accent link – used sparingly */
a {
  color: #6aa6ff;
  text-decoration: none;
}
a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

/* ── Trigger button (toggle file browser) ── */
.trigger {
  padding: 8px 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: #3a3d41;
  border: none;
  color: inherit;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.trigger:hover {
  background: #45494d;
}

/* ── Native <dialog> styling ── */
.browser-dialog {
  background: #252526;
  color: #e6e6e6;
  border: 1px solid #3c3c3c;
  border-radius: 8px;
  max-width: 960px;
  width: 90vw;
  padding: 16px;
  /* Remove default UA margin/padding */
  margin: auto;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.browser-dialog::backdrop {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
}

/* ── Header row ── */
.dialog-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.dialog-header h2 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.dialog-header .close-btn {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: #9a9a9a;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1;
  padding: 4px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
.dialog-header .close-btn:hover {
  color: #e6e6e6;
  background: #2d2d30;
}

/* ── Toolbar ── */
.toolbar {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

/* Breadcrumb */
.breadcrumb {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.breadcrumb a {
  color: #9a9a9a;
  font-size: 13px;
}
.breadcrumb a:hover {
  color: #e6e6e6;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.breadcrumb .separator {
  color: #3c3c3c;
  margin: 0 2px;
}

/* Search input */
.toolbar input[type="search"],
.toolbar input[type="text"] {
  background: #333337;
  color: #e6e6e6;
  border: 1px solid #3c3c3c;
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  font-size: 13px;
  outline: none;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.toolbar input[type="search"]::placeholder,
.toolbar input[type="text"]::placeholder {
  color: #9a9a9a;
}
.toolbar input[type="search"]:focus,
.toolbar input[type="text"]:focus {
  border-color: #6aa6ff;
}

/* Upload label styled as button */
.toolbar label.upload-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 6px 12px;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: #3a3d41;
  border: none;
  color: inherit;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 13px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.toolbar label.upload-btn:hover {
  background: #45494d;
}
.toolbar label.upload-btn input[type="file"] {
  display: none;
}

/* ── Results container (scrollable) ── */
.results-container {
  max-height: 60vh;
  overflow: auto;
  border: 1px solid #3c3c3c;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

/* ── Table ── */
.results-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  table-layout: auto;
}
.results-table th,
.results-table td {
  padding: 6px 8px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #3c3c3c;
  text-align: left;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.results-table th {
  color: #9a9a9a;
  font-weight: 500;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  background: #252526;
  z-index: 1;
}
.results-table tbody tr:hover {
  background: #2d2d30;
}

/* Folder rows – slightly heavier weight */
.results-table .folder-row td {
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ── Small action buttons ── */
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: #3a3d41;
  border: none;
  color: inherit;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 12px;
  line-height: 1.4;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn:hover {
  background: #45494d;
}
.btn:disabled {
  opacity: 0.5;
  cursor: default;
}
.btn:disabled:hover {
  background: #3a3d41;
}

/* ── Status footer ── */
.status {
  margin-top: 8px;
  color: #9a9a9a;
  font-size: 12px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

```
Create src/app.css (it will be copied to wwwroot/dist/app.css by the build). A muted dark theme only — no bright/neon colors. Suggested palette: body background #1e1e1e, text #e6e6e6, panels/dialog #252526, borders #3c3c3c, hover #2d2d30, muted text #9a9a9a, subtle accent link color #6aa6ff (used sparingly). Style at minimum: body (system font stack, margin 0, color/background, font-size 14px); the trigger button `.trigger` (padding, cursor pointer, background #3a3d41, border none, color inherit, border-radius 4px, hover #45494d); the native `<dialog>` via `.browser-dialog` (background #252526, color #e6e6e6, border 1px solid #3c3c3c, border-radius 8px, max-width 960px, width 90vw, padding 16px) and `.browser-dialog::backdrop` (background rgba(0,0,0,0.6)); a header row (flex space-between, title left, close button right); a `.toolbar` (flex wrap gap, breadcrumb `.breadcrumb a` styling, a search `<input>` with dark background #333337 and light text, an upload label styled like a button); a results `<table>` (width 100%, border-collapse, `th`/`td` padding 6px 8px, bottom border 1px solid #3c3c3c, `tbody tr:hover` background #2d2d30, `th` left-aligned muted); folder name rows slightly heavier weight; `.btn` small action buttons (reuse button styling); `.status` footer muted text with counts/sizes; ensure nothing overflows and the table is scrollable if tall (max-height on the results container with overflow:auto). Keep it minimal and clean. Verify: the file exists at src/app.css and will be referenced by index.html as dist/app.css.

## Response Format (required)
Respond with ONLY a single valid JSON object matching the schema below.
- No prose, explanations, or commentary before or after the JSON.
- No markdown code fences (```), no headings — output the raw JSON object.
- Do NOT call any tools and do NOT end your turn on a thinking block. Emit the JSON object directly as text.

JSON schema:
{ approved: Whether the implementation is accepted, feedback: Detailed review feedback, issues: Array<{ file: File with the issue, description: What needs to be fixed, severity: "critical" | "minor" /* How important the fix is */ }> }

{
  "approved": true,
  "feedback": "The src/app.css implementation is complete and faithfully matches every requirement in the task description. All specified palette colors are present and correct (body #1e1e1e, text #e6e6e6, panels/dialog #252526, borders #3c3c3c, hover #2d2d30, muted text #9a9a9a, accent #6aa6ff used sparingly only on links). All required components are styled: body (system font stack, margin 0, 14px, dark bg), .trigger button, .browser-dialog with proper backdrop, header row (flex space-between with title/close button), .toolbar (flex wrap gap), breadcrumb links, search input (#333337 bg, light text, focus accent border), upload label styled as button, results table (100% width, border-collapse, proper padding/borders, sticky muted th, hover rows), folder rows with heavier weight (font-weight 600), .btn action buttons, and .status footer. The scrollable container uses max-height: 60vh with overflow: auto and the th is correctly sticky with a background color to avoid transparency bleed-through. The theme is muted/dark with no neon. Code is well-organized with clear section comments. The minor duplication of button styles (#3a3d41 bg / #45494d hover / border-radius) across .trigger, .upload-btn, and .btn is standard CSS practice for distinct components and not worth flagging. Note: verification of the index.html → dist/app.css reference is a build/integration concern outside this file's scope and was not reviewable from the provided snippet, but the file content itself satisfies the task.",
  "issues": []
}
